{"word":"G2662 - καταπατέω - katapatéō - kat-ap-at-eh'-o - Trample","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταπατέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katapatéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ap-at-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Trample</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மிதி"},{"paragraph":"to tread down trample under foot"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3961 - πατέω - patéō - pat-eh'-o/3961\">G3961</a>; to <i>trample down</i>; figuratively to <i>reject</i> with disdain: - trample, tread (down, underfoot).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1704/1704\">G1704</a>, <a href=\"#/G2662/2662\">G2662</a>, <a href=\"#/G3961/3961\">G3961</a>, <a href=\"#/G4043/4043\">G4043</a>"}]}